item.title: I just want to say...THANK YOU!
item.description:
I just want to say...THANK YOU!
I realize that the numbers change often and that I make a video EVERYDAY which helps in getting more views and even though the numbers are not what are really important it is a great reward and validation to the time we devote to making these videos and I hope you guys will allow me just a little opportunity to express how I feel very thank full and excited about how well the daily vlogs have done. It's almost UNIMAGINABLE that I have made a video everyday for the last 327 days and that you guys have stuck with us. It's not well produced or well edited and I am the FIRST to realize..."Hey, this is just some tubby dude hanging out with his friends and family" But you guys continue to watch and share in our lives and I am very grateful for that! Sorry if I am all lovey dovey sappy or whatever. Mile Sur Mera Tumhara is an Iconic video focusing on national integration and unity in diversity. The song, Mile Sur Mera Tumhara was created in 1988 and aired on 15th August (Independence Day) on Doordarshan. Mile Sur Mera Tumhara featured National icons like Amitabh Bachchan, Sunil Gavaskar, Kapil Dev, Kamal Hassan, Lata Mangeshkar, Pt. Bhimsen Joshi and many more. item.title: Minnesota Vikings vs New Orleans Saints 28 - 31 Highlights - NFL Playoffs 2010
item.description:
Minnesota Vikings vs New Orleans Saints 28 - 31 Highlights - NFL Playoffs 2010
http://www.watch-live-nfl.com/ Garrett Hartley nailed a 40-yard field goal on the Saints' first possession of overtime to send New Orleans to its first Super Bowl. The Vikings had a chance to win in regulation but Brett Favre threw an interception with 12 seconds left deep in Saints territory. Saints LB Jonathan Vilma led a defense that hurried Brett Favre all day and forced five turnovers. Vilma had one of the Saints' two interceptions and forced a fumble in the third quarter. The Vikings dominated in every major statistical category, but the Saints kept the game close by forcing six fumbles and two interceptions Minnesota Vikings vs New Orleans Saints - Highlights - NFL Playoffs 2010 "Vikings vs Saints" "Vikings vs Saints Highlights" "Vikings vs Saints 2010 Playoffs" B.Favre "brett favre" brett favre peyton manning "peyton manning"
